e></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kyf1665702740049.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kyf1665702740049.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kyf1665702740049.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kyf1665702740049\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $logical\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"kyf1665702740049___logical_274323\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the value of an application logical.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__topic_d85862e1_d85863e1_d85864e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__p_d85865e1_d85866e1_d85867e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$logical</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__section_w210ab1b7b5_w211ab1b7_w212ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__p_d85868e1_d85869e1_d85870e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vDir = $logical(\"export_dir\")</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__topic_d57072e1_d57073e1_d57074e1_d57075e1_d57076e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d134206e81\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__table_d9068e1_d9069e1_d9070e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__table_d9068e1_d9069e1_d9070e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__table_d9068e1_d9069e1_d9070e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__table_d9068e1_d9069e1_d9070e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kyf1665702740049__table_d9068e1_d9069e1_d9070e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kyf1665702740049__table_d9068e1_d9069e1_d9070e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kyf1665702740049__table_d9068e1_d9069e1_d9070e1__entry__3\">\n Name of a logical symbol defined in the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__topic_d57077e1_d57078e1_d57079e1_d57080e1_d57081e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d134206e135\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__li_d34742e1_d34743e1_d34744e1\">Value associated with the logical symbol name.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__li_d34745e1_d34746e1_d34747e1\">Empty string (<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>), if <var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalName</var> is not found.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__topic_d57082e1_d57083e1_d57084e1_d57085e1_d57086e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d134206e157\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__p_d85880e1_d85881e1_d85882e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__section_nyc_kvb_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d134206e166\">Example: Setting Directory Locations in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">You can use logicals to allow you to spawn platform-specific commands.\n               Consider the following section in an assignment file:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__pre_jnp_kvb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[LOGICALS]\nwork_directory = c:/my_app/test/work</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">This logical symbol can be used in ProcScript to refer to the\n               appropriate directory:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__pre_knp_kvb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">WorkDir = $logical(\"work_directory\")\nSubDir = \"%%$logical(\"work_directory\")%%%/axel\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The results of these statements are:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__ul_lnp_kvb_1cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__li_d34748e1_d34749e1_d34750e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">WorkDir</code> contains\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">c:/my_app/test/work</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__li_d34751e1_d34752e1_d34753e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">SubDir</code> contains\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">c:/my_app/test/work/axel</code>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__section_ksg_hvb_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d134206e210\">Example: Enabling the Debugger in a Deployed Application</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">To enable the debugger to be started in a deployed application:</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__ol_nqt_hvb_1cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__li_d34754e1_d34755e1_d34756e1\">Add the following ProcScript to the\n                  keyboardSwitch trigger of the application\n                  shell:<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__pre_oqt_hvb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger keyboardSwitch \nif ($logical(\"SwitchKeyboard\") = \"debug\")\n debug\nendif\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kyf1665702740049__li_d34757e1_d34758e1_d34759e1\">If debugging is required for some reason in\n                  the deployed application, add <code class=\"ph codeph\">SwitchKeyboard=debug</code> to the\n                  [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file, and activate the trigger by pressing\n                  GOLD Y.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vcm1665702739978.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[LOGICALS]</a><p>Use the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file to assign values to logicals that can be accessed using the $logical ProcScript function. Each application can have its own set of logicals.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529434\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529434\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$logical Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $logical Return the value of an application logical. $logical ( LogicalName ) Example: vDir = $logical(\"export_dir\") Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description LogicalName String Name of a logical symbol defined in the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file. Return Values Value associated with the logical symbol name. Empty string ( \"\" ), if LogicalName is not found. Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Setting Directory Locations in ProcScript You can use logicals to allow you to spawn platform-specific commands. Consider the following section in an assignment file: [LOGICALS] work_directory = c:/my_app/test/work Copy This logical symbol can be used in ProcScript to refer to the appropriate directory: WorkDir = $logical(\"work_directory\") SubDir = \"%%$logical(\"work_directory\")%%%/axel\" Copy The results of these statements are: WorkDir contains c:/my_app/test/work SubDir contains c:/my_app/test/work/axel Example: Enabling the Debugger in a Deployed Application To enable the debugger to be started in a deployed application: Add the following ProcScript to the keyboardSwitch trigger of the application shell: trigger keyboardSwitch if ($logical(\"SwitchKeyboard\") = \"debug\") debug endif end Copy If debugging is required for some reason in the deployed application, add SwitchKeyboard=debug to the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file, and activate the trigger by pressing GOLD Y. Related Links [LOGICALS] Use the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file to assign values to logicals that can be accessed using the $logical ProcScript function. Each application can have its own set of logicals. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}